_sText: AIM_CENTRALPOINT Well the name came from nowhere :) This is a aim_map wich has a lot of itense gaming, It gives a chance to the player to rush or long rage shooting. Also has a Buyzone and a Bombsite on the middle, you can go there by the airbridge acessing from both Spawns. The map is balanced, a good modern/futurist architecture, and good gameplay. Players spawn with a Deagle, knives, and a Frag Grenade. Every time the round starts thats what you will get by losing or wining the last round. This map includes a 3DSkyBox. The File comes with a auto generated Nav. file. This map is pr0^^ and I is not lier! =D Have Fun Aim it
